# Gmail OAuth — Google Cloud Console → APIs & Services → Credentials
# 1) Enable Gmail API for the project
# 2) Create OAuth client ID type "Web application"
# 3) Authorized redirect URI must match GMAIL_REDIRECT_URI exactly (your dev URL + /api/auth/gmail/callback)
# The app requests Gmail read/send + OpenID profile (name/email). Re-sign if scopes change.
# Your browser gets a session cookie after Gmail OAuth so APIs use the same InsForge user as your inbox.
GMAIL_CLIENT_ID=
GMAIL_CLIENT_SECRET=
GMAIL_REDIRECT_URI=http://localhost:3000/api/auth/gmail/callback
# Optional: used to build direct Google API enable links in UI warnings
GCP_PROJECT_ID=1080606790388